I was born where silence met a glowing screen,
Curious eyes chasing codes yet unseen.
From broken lines and errors in red,
I built my dreams where logic led.

Through sleepless nights and coffee-stained keys,
I spoke to machines with growing ease.
Each bug I faced became my guide,
Turning doubt into strength inside.

Now I create in a digital sea,
A world of tech that began with me.

